1. *Usta* su mi se smešila u osmeh (My lips curled into a smile)
2. Ona je ljubila *usta* svog deteta (She kissed her child's lips)
3. On je zatvorio *usta* i ćutao (He closed his mouth and kept quiet)
4. Ljudi su visoko podigli *usta* u znak podrške (People raised their voices high in support)
5. Njen pogled je prešao preko *usta* (Her gaze passed over his lips)
6. Ona je stavila prst na *usta* da bi zaštitila tajnu (She put her finger on her lips to protect the secret)